"(S, A, O, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aboHN","text_ar":"شَبْحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$axoSN","text_ar":"شَخْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"body,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bodily"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corporeal form"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"figure"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"substance, of a man"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"some other thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"object, which one sees from a distance"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, A, O, Msb, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a man,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"some other creature, of which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$axoS","text_ar":"شَخْص"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"body,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appears to one:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that is perceived by sense"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, O, L) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by sight:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, L:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$obaAHN","text_ar":"اَشْبَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, O, Msb, K,) which is of the former, (A, Msb,) and [of the latter]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ubuwHN","text_ar":"شُبُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laAHa liY $abaHN","text_ar":"لَاحَ لِى شَبَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$axoSN","text_ar":"شَخْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A body,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bodily form, appeared, loomed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gleamed, to me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo A^a$obaAHN bilaA A^arowaAHK","text_ar":"هُمْ اَشْبَاحٌ بِلَا اَرْوَاحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They are bodies without souls"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a*aq~u mino $abaHK","text_ar":"اَذَقُّ مِنْ شَبَحٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baATilK","text_ar":"بَاطِلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, O,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino xayoTi baATilK","text_ar":"مِنْ خَيْطِ بَاطِلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a prov., (O,) meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"More minute,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inconsiderable, than"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the atoms that are seen in the rays of the sun entering from a mural aperture in a chamber:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, * O:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"than the thread that comes forth from the mouth of the spider;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gossamer;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"called by the children"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxaATN","text_ar":"مُخَاطٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~ayoTaAni","text_ar":"الشَّيْطَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^asomaA='u DarobaAni A^asomaA='u A^a$obaAHK","text_ar":"الاَسْمَا=ءُ ضَرْبَانِ اَسْمَا=ءُ اَشْبَاحٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA^asomaA='u A^aEomaAlK","text_ar":"وَاَسْمَا=ءُ اَعْمَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Nouns are of two sorts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the names of things perceived by sense, and the names"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of actions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or rather"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of accidents"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attributes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of other things;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as they say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asomaA='u AlA^aEoyaAni","text_ar":"اَسْمَا=ءُ الاَعْيَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asomaA='u AlmaEaAniY","text_ar":"اَسْمَا=ءُ المَعَانِى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"halaka","text_ar":"هَلَكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$obaAHu maAlihi","text_ar":"اَشْبَاحُ مَالِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The known ones of his camels, and sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats, and other cattle, perished."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K. *)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abaHN","text_ar":"شَبَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A door"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gate, of high structure;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aboHN","text_ar":"شَبْحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) [but the latter may have originated from a mistranscription; for Sgh says,] and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abajN","text_ar":"شَبَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.)       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abaHapN","text_ar":"شَبَحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","A","O","Msb","K","L"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}